data.enText: lasting or intended to last or be used only for a short time; not permanent
I'm looking for some temporary work .

data.chText: 他们不得不搬进临时住所。
data.enText: They had to move into temporary accommodation .

data.chText: 临时措施 / 解决办法 / 安排
半数以上的职员是临时雇员。
data.enText: More than half the staff are temporary.

data.chText: 我们很抱歉暂时不能提供这一服务。
data.enText: We regret this service is temporarily unavailable.

simple_means.memory_skill: tempor 时间象 + ary 物 → 有时间性的 → 临时的

tr: a worker (especially in an office) hired on a temporary basis

example: politics is an impermanent factor of life"- James Thurbe

value.def: Something that is temporary lasts for only a limited time.

example.ex: His job here is only temporary...
example.tran: 他在这儿的工作只是临时的。
多数青少年问题是暂时性的。

example.ex: The peace agreement has at least temporarily halted the civil war...
example.tran: 该和平协定至少暂时停止了内战。

example.ex: Checkpoints between the two zones were temporarily closed.
example.tran: 那两个地区之间的检查站被临时关闭。
